      <title>Samsung Has New Tablet Ready For Pre Order At Amazon</title>
      <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/GulfstreamNews/~3/0xugya8stjE/</link>
      <comments>http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/samsung-has-new-tablet-ready-for-pre-order-at-amazon/7399/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Oct 2011 14:32:48 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>BEHydek</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Featured News]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Tablet]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Amazon Pre order]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy Tab 7.0 Plus]]></category>
      <category><![CDATA[tablet announcement]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/?p=7399</guid>
      <description>// The Samsung Galaxy Tab 7.0 Plus is ready for pre-order at Amazon. As long as the shopper dosen&amp;#8217;t mind the under $400 price tag. The tablet with the 7-inch touchscreen will feature Honey Comb 3.2 and the TouchWiz interface. Driven by a 1.2GHz dual-core CPU and powered by Android 3.2 (Honeycomb), the Galaxy Tab from Samsung [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/gulfstream-news/Gulfstream_News-Samsung_Has_New_Tablet_Ready_For_Pre_Order_At_Amazon.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><div style="float: left; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"><script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[
 google_ad_client = "pub-1450538712102813"; /* 300x250, created 4/26/11 */ google_ad_slot = "5911278597"; google_ad_width = 300; google_ad_height = 250;
// ]]&gt;</script><br />
<script src="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js" type="text/javascript">
</script></div>
<div id="attachment_7403" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 188px">
	<a href="http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/GALAXY-Tab-7.0-Plus-Product-Image-test.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-7403" title="Samsung Has New Tablet Ready For Pre Order At Amazon" src="http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/GALAXY-Tab-7.0-Plus-Product-Image-test.jpg" alt="Samsung Has New Tablet Ready For Pre Order At Amazon" width="188" height="130" /></a>
	<p class="wp-caption-text">Samsung Has New Tablet Ready For Pre Order At Amazon - Samsung</p>
</div>
<p>The <strong>Samsung Galaxy Tab 7.0 Plus </strong>is ready for pre-order at Amazon. As long as the shopper dosen&#8217;t mind the under $400 price tag. The tablet with the 7-inch touchscreen will feature Honey Comb 3.2 and the TouchWiz interface.</p>
<p>Driven by a 1.2GHz dual-core CPU and powered by Android 3.2  (Honeycomb), the Galaxy Tab from Samsung gives the user quick responses  when launching apps. The 7-inch WSVGA touchscreen compliments its  powerful yet slim design. The tablet  allows connectivity via USB and  Bluetooth slots as well as 3G and Wi-Fi.</p>
<p>The new 7-inch Galaxy tablet will feature the ability to use the new Peel Smart Remote App which will allow the user to control most home entertainment system via infrared capability regardless of who manufactured the hardware. This timely app has just been released.</p>
<p>The Galaxy Tab 7.0 Plus has both front (2MP) and rear (3MP) digital cameras.  The electronic gadget will come preloaded with Samsung&#8217;s Hubs including  Music and Reader giving the user a huge selection of music, books,  newspapers, and magazines in which to be informed and entertained.  Interested in experiencing this tablet for all it can do?<a rel="nofollow" href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB005N1333M%2Fref%3Das_li_ss_tl%3Fie%3DUTF8%26amp%3Btag%3Donthewebnow-20%26amp%3BlinkCode%3Das2%26amp%3Bcamp%3D217145%26amp%3Bcreative%3D399373%26amp%3BcreativeASIN%3DB005N1333M&sref=rss">Click here to pre order the Samsung Galaxy Tab 7-Inch Tablet </a><img style="border: none !important; margin: 0px !important;" src="http://www.assoc-amazon.com/e/ir?t=onthewebnow-20&amp;l=as2&amp;o=1&amp;a=B005N1333M&amp;camp=217145&amp;creative=399373" border="0" alt="" width="1" height="1" /><br />
(from the US Amazon). <a rel="nofollow" href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesswire.com%2Fnews%2Fhome%2F20111021005961%2Fen%2FSamsung-Expands-U.S.-Tablet-Portfolio-Galaxy-Tab&sref=rss">Click here</a> for more details on the tablet from Samsung.</p>
