      <description>// The Motorola Admiral will be available to some Sprint customers online for ordering as early as Oct. 23rd. The smartphone will feature the new Direct Connect feature from Sprint. The new addition will offer its user an Android powered push-to-talk capability. The Admiral from Motorola and using the Sprint network, will be powered by [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/gulfstream-news/Gulfstream_News-Motorola_Admiral_Will_Lead_The_Way_With_Sprint_Direct_Connect.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
