      <description>// T-Mobile has put up a sign-up page on their site for email notifications for the T-Mobile SpringBoard with Google tablet computer. The listing shows that the tablet will have a 7-inch HD touch display and will come preloaded with Netflix and Blockbuster apps. A release put out by the carrier says that it will [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/gulfstream-news/Gulfstream_News-Carrier_Is_Closer_to_Release_Of_SpringBoard_Android_Tablet.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
