      <description>// The Samsung Stratosphere will make its online appearance at Verizon Wireless on October 13. The smartphone will be the carriers first 4G/LTE (with QWERTY keyboard) entry into the market. The mobile device may be available in selected stores on or about the same date for around $150 (after a mail-in rebate) with agreement. The [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/gulfstream-news/Gulfstream_News-Samsung_Stratosphere__Reaching_The_Heights_Via_4GLTE.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
