<div id="attachment_7372" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 130px">
	<a href="http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/SamsungStratosphere-test.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-7372" title="Samsung Stratosphere - Reaching The Heights Via 4G/LTE" src="http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/SamsungStratosphere-test.jpg" alt="Samsung Stratosphere - Reaching The Heights Via 4G/LTE" width="130" height="252" /></a>
	<p class="wp-caption-text">Samsung Stratosphere - Reaching The Heights Via 4G/LTE - Image Verizon Wireless</p>
</div>
<p>The <strong>Samsung Stratosphere </strong>will make its online appearance at Verizon Wireless on October 13. The smartphone will be the carriers first 4G/LTE (with QWERTY keyboard) entry into the market. The mobile device may be available in selected stores on or about the same date for around $150 (after a mail-in rebate) with agreement.</p>
<p>The Stratosphere by Samsung is powered by a 1GHz Cortez Hummingbird CPU and will be running on Android 2.3 or &#8216;Gingerbread&#8217;. The smartphone is also a new sibling in the Samsung Galaxy S family of cell phones. The powerful mobile device will feature a slide out full 5-row QWERTY keyboard and a 4-inch super AMOLED display.</p>
<p>The Stratosphere will showcase support for mobile Business to Business or B2B Cisco AnyConnect  enhanced connectivity services. These services will enhance the ability of the user for such apps as Microsoft Exchange AciveSync or EAS and other services. The smartphone will have two digital cameras, a front-facing 1.3MP and a 5MP camera for shooting still images and 720p digital video .</p>
<p>The smartphone will be able to connect via Bluetooth, Wi-Fi, or the Verizon network. the mobile device will have such business services as Support for Sybase Afaria and encryption services that should be able to satisfy most IT departments.   <a href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Ffirst-4g-lte-smartphone-with-qwerty-keyboard-for-verizon-wireless-the-samsung-stratosphere-131442533.html&sref=rss">Click here</a> for more details on the Samsung Stratosphere.</p>
