      <description>// Samsung has brought the Transform Ultra, a new Android smartphone to Boost Mobile. The new mobile device will join the Galaxy Prevail that has become Samsung&amp;#8217;s bestselling smartphone of the last four months. The Transform will sell for under $230. The Transform Ultra from Samsung is powered by a 1GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon CPU and [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/gulfstream-news/Gulfstream_News-New_Samsung_Smartphone_Will_Transform_At_Boost_Mobile.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
