      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/?p=7322</guid>
      <description>// The Casio G&amp;#8217;zOne Commando is finally joining the other smartphones in getting the current popular update of the Android operating system. Along with other various updates and fixes put out by Verizon, the Android 2.3 shows its face for the rugged mobile device.  The improvements in the update include such things as: screen will [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/gulfstream-news/Gulfstream_News-Casio_GzOne_Commando_Joins_The_Gingerbread_Crowd.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><div style="float: left; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"><script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[
    google_ad_client = "pub-1450538712102813"; /* 300x250, created 4/26/11 */ google_ad_slot = "5911278597"; google_ad_width = 300; google_ad_height = 250;
// ]]&gt;</script><br />
<script src="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js" type="text/javascript">
</script></div>
<div id="attachment_6136" class="wp-caption alignright" style="width: 130px">
	<a href="http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Amazon-CasioCommando-test.jpg"><img class=" " title="Casio G'zOne Commando Joins The Gingerbread Crowd" src="http://gulfstreamcleaning.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/Amazon-CasioCommando-test.jpg" alt="Casio G'zOne Commando Joins The Gingerbread Crowd" width="130" height="226" /></a>
	<p class="wp-caption-text">Casio G&#39;zOne Commando Joins The Gingerbread Crowd</p>
</div>
<p>The <strong>Casio G&#8217;zOne Commando </strong>is finally joining the other smartphones in getting the current popular update of the Android operating system. Along with other various updates and fixes put out by Verizon, the Android 2.3 shows its face for the rugged mobile device.  The improvements in the update include such things as: screen will brighten when a phone call is received while being docked and auto-signature can be enabled for SMS/MMS messages.<a rel="nofollow" href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.verizonwireless.com%2Fpdf%2Fsystem_update%2Fcommando.pdf&sref=rss"> Click here </a>for more information on this new update.</p>
<p>Recently the tough gadget was showing its toughness in an &#8216;extreme&#8217; campaign.The <a href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.multivu.com%2Fmnr%2F51201-casio-launches-tougher-is-smarter-campaign&sref=rss">promotion</a> features the smartphone in six different scenarios showing that it is durable and can withstand things that would make other mobile devices cease to function. The scenarios feature the smartphone, on a surfboard, on a dirt bike, on a rugged outdoor trail, in an off road rally, getting punched by a boxer, etc.</p>
<p>The Gingerbread OS driven <a href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazonwireless.com%2Fdp%2FB004XDDOPI%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26amp%3Btag%3Donthewebnow-20%26amp%3BlinkCode%3Dxm2%26amp%3Bcamp%3D1789%26amp%3BcreativeASIN%3DB004XDDOPI&sref=rss">G&#8217;zOne Commando</a> from Casio, with network support from Verizon Wireless. The rugged handset running on Android 2.3 is ready for whatever mission you throw at it. Meeting Military Standards 810G, the user can rest assured that whether they are involved in an active lifestyle or being a road warrior this cell phone can handle it.</p>
<p>The Casio Gz&#8217;One Commando can resist rain, shock, vibration, as well as low and high temperatures. This smartphone may be the ideal communication tool for construction, warehouses, and hazardous areas. This may indeed be the right gadget to have if the user needs to download blueprints, update project plans, or for other management type duties.</p>
<p>The Casio Commando can also resist fog, solar radiation, and dust; allowing the person with an active lifestyle to go anywhere and know that they have one tough smartphone. The Commando can also be a Mobile Hotspot and share a 3G connection with up to five Wi-Fi capable devices. The smartphone has a 5MP digital camera with autofocus and LED flash. <a rel="nofollow" href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazonwireless.com%2Fdp%2FB004XDDOPI%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26amp%3Btag%3Donthewebnow-20%26amp%3BlinkCode%3Dxm2%26amp%3Bcamp%3D1789%26amp%3BcreativeASIN%3DB004XDDOPI&sref=rss">Click here</a> for more details on the Casio Gz&#8217;One Commando.   <a rel="nofollow" href="http://redirectingat.com?id=10040X685899&xs=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.multivu.com%2Fmnr%2F51201-casio-launches-tougher-is-smarter-campaign&sref=rss">Click here for more information on the promotion</a>.</p>
